not-so refreshing for the murkors.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/70ca5f32df1f7b94642bff54348b48c6.poster.avif?t=1741788194\" width=596 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/70ca5f32df1f7b94642bff54348b48c6.webm?t=1741788194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/70ca5f32df1f7b94642bff54348b48c6.mp4?t=1741788194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/674c58717cd04c4f4948c4306efc136e.avif?t=1741788194\" width=596 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect ‘Mucus’ dropped by Murkors as they are defeated - this will become the currency you can bank. With ‘Mucus’ in the bank you can progress level-trees and make yourself stronger on every run. That’s right, defender… Death is not the end for you! <i>(Or so we’ve been told to tell you. Just go and defend earth)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/d8ea96681de4ea743b02ab14a37fbf4b.poster.avif?t=1741788194\" width=596 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/d8ea96681de4ea743b02ab14a37fbf4b.webm?t=1741788194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440010/extras/d8ea96681de4ea743b02ab14a37fbf4b.mp4?t=1741788194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
